::DarkMouse::

She went flying across the room when Megatron struck her.  She slid 
across the floor a few feet and stopped.  She got up shaking from the 
hit.  She wasn't expecting it.  She slowly walked over to Megatron.
"Commander, she will sleep with the drug in her for a while.  We can 
tie her to a table in Scorponok's lab.  When she wakes, she will see 
her situation and be more likely to talk."
